      <title>配置优化过程</title>
      <link href="/2022/0125/043300/"/>
      <url>/2022/0125/043300/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="零、快速开始"><a href="#零、快速开始" class="headerlink" title="零、快速开始"></a>零、快速开始</h1><h1 id="一、增加功能"><a href="#一、增加功能" class="headerlink" title="一、增加功能"></a>一、增加功能</h1><h1 id="二、主题特色化-amp-优化"><a href="#二、主题特色化-amp-优化" class="headerlink" title="二、主题特色化&amp;优化"></a>二、主题特色化&amp;优化</h1><p>TOC：Table of Contents，HEXO自带了TOC生成功能，在文章头里可以设置开启/关闭，主题配置文件可设置展开级数，自动收缩等(ctrl+F:TOC)。</p><h2 id="2、页"><a href="#2、页" class="headerlink" title="2、页"></a>2、页</h2><pre class="line-numbers language-bash" data-language="bash"><code class="language-bash">hexo new page <span class="token string">"categories"</span>   <span class="token comment">#分类页</span>hexo new page <span class="token string">"tags"</span>         <span class="token comment">#标签</span>hexo new page <span class="token string">"about"</span>        <span class="token comment">#关于</span>hexo new page <span class="token string">"friends"</span>      <span class="token comment">#友情链接</span>hexo new page <span class="token string">"contact"</span>      <span class="token comment">#留言</span>``<span class="token variable"><span class="token variable">`</span>  <span class="token comment"># 三、安装的插件</span>+ 安装过的插件+ 安装命令及相关配置+ 过程中遇到的问题  通过npm list<span class="token comment">## 1、dplayer</span>dplayer是用来在网页中插入视频的，安装命令:  <span class="token variable">`</span></span>`<span class="token variable"><span class="token variable">`</span><span class="token function">bash</span><span class="token function">npm</span> <span class="token function">install</span> dplayer <span class="token variable">`</span></span>`<span class="token variable"><span class="token variable">`</span>  <span class="token comment">### 1.2 问题  </span>有些解析不了。。。  <span class="token comment">## 2、hexo-math  </span>用来显示数学公式  <span class="token variable">`</span></span>``bash<span class="token function">npm</span> <span class="token function">install</span> hexo-math --save<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><h3 id="2-1-MathML语言与LaTxt"><a href="#2-1-MathML语言与LaTxt" class="headerlink" title="2.1 MathML语言与LaTxt"></a>2.1 MathML语言与LaTxt</h3><p><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/ViatorSun/article/details/82826664">超详细 LaTex数学公式</a><br><a href="https://www.zybuluo.com/knight/note/96093">2</a></p><h2 id="3、搜索"><a href="#3、搜索" class="headerlink" title="3、搜索"></a>3、搜索</h2><p>在博客中增加内容搜索</p><pre class="line-numbers language-bash" data-language="bash"><code class="language-bash"><span class="token function">npm</span> <span class="token function">install</span> hexo-generator-search --save<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><p>在 Hexo 根目录下的<code>_config.yml</code>文件中，新增以下的配置项:</p><pre class="line-numbers language-yml" data-language="yml"><code class="language-yml">search:  path: search.xml  field: post<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><h2 id="4、字数统计"><a href="#4、字数统计" class="headerlink" title="4、字数统计"></a>4、字数统计</h2><p>在文章中显示文章字数、阅读时长信息</p><pre class="line-numbers language-bash" data-language="bash"><code class="language-bash"><span class="token function">npm</span> i --save hexo-wordcount``<span class="token variable"><span class="token variable">`</span>   根目录下的<span class="token variable">`</span></span>_config.yml<span class="token variable"><span class="token variable">`</span>文件中，新增以下的配置项:   <span class="token variable">`</span></span>``ymlwordCount:  enable: <span class="token boolean">false</span>         <span class="token comment"># 将这个值设置为 true 即可.</span>  postWordCount: <span class="token boolean">true</span>   <span class="token comment">#字数统计</span>  min2read: <span class="token boolean">true</span>        <span class="token comment"># 阅读时长预计</span>  totalCount: <span class="token boolean">true</span>      <span class="token comment">#网站总字数</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><h1 id="四、部署到腾讯云"><a href="#四、部署到腾讯云" class="headerlink" title="四、部署到腾讯云"></a>四、部署到腾讯云</h1><p><code>npm i -g @cloudbase/cli hexo-cli</code><br><code>cloudbase hosting deploy public -e blog-8grg2mls20371f76</code>  ps:[环境id]</p><h1 id="五、markdown补充"><a href="#五、markdown补充" class="headerlink" title="五、markdown补充"></a>五、markdown补充</h1><pre class="line-numbers language-html" data-language="html"><code class="language-html"><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class="token attr-name">align</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation attr-equals">=</span>center</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>  #居中对齐<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><p>空格：<br><code>&amp;emsp;</code>&emsp;表示一个中文空格<br>&amp;ensp;&emsp;表示装修个中文空格<br><code>$~~~~~~$</code>$~~~~~~$能实现，对不齐  </p>]]></content>
      
      
